   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"The holy seventh year of Nero Claudius Caesar Augustus Germanicus Imperator. He has worked in the Pholemis canal for five days on the dikes for the same year, on behalf of Theadelphia: Aunes, son of Harthotes. (2nd hand) I, Harpaesis, have signed on behalf of Aunes, son of Harthotes. (3rd hand) I, Herakleides, antigrapheus from the (office of) strategos Philoxenos have signed. (4th hand) I, Euhemeros, antigrapheus of the (office of) the basilikogrammateus have signed."</ab>
         </div>
